<!--  **************************************************************************
      SPECIAL NOTE: 
	This DTD was modified for the Arbortext implementation.
      Changes:
      20030116 modified to reference the latest version of 38784 (Draft V7 to 
               include updated support for the change application)
      20030117 created three row wrapper for semantic tables:
                 consumrow in consumtab
                 referrow in refertab
                 jgindexrow in jgindextab
               changed the contents of the related table to be the row wrapper, 
               and moved the contents into the new row wrapper element
      20040220 Added ATTLIST to content models:
                 refertab
                 foldouts
      20040220 - removed 38784 subset in favor of an entity to 38784 directory
               - added %chgatt to the following:
                 chapno          chap            fobrk     
                 func            funcno          functitle     
                 funtitle        sssn            toc  
               - changed #PCDATA content model to %text; in the following:
                 persreq     
      ********************************************************************** -->

